# Cloud boot (core)

- Read `AGENTS.md` and route work into exactly one category folder: `simulation/`, `data-analysis/`, `literature/`, `writing/`, `course-prep/`, or `chore/`. Put shared libraries in `shared/`.
- Cloud agents only see files in this git repo — do not assume laptop-only paths exist.
- Keep `.cursor/environment.json` lean. Do not install HPC/GPU stacks here unless the task truly needs them in this environment.
- After plot-related changes, run `python3 data-analysis/example_scientific_plot.py`.
